2Ô∏è‚É£ region_growth_analysis(df)

Calculates growth rate over time:

Growth % =
(Current Period Sales - Previous Period Sales)
/ Previous Period Sales √ó 100

Helps detect expanding or declining regions.

3Ô∏è‚É£ region_profitability_analysis(df)

Computes revenue and estimated profit by region.

Revenue =
Units Sold √ó Price √ó (1 - Discount)

Profit =
Revenue - Estimated Cost

4Ô∏è‚É£ region_demand_volatility(df)

Calculates standard deviation of demand by region.

High volatility ‚Üí Higher safety stock needed.

5Ô∏è‚É£ region_stock_efficiency(df)

Measures:

Units Sold / Inventory Level

Indicates inventory utilization efficiency.

